<br>
I'm not knocking the SK class, that's just the way it is. SKs die more often than not pulling raid-level critters.  Monks die, too, just less often than any other class.  Hell, for xp'ing, I FAR prefer grouping with SK's and having the SK pull.  Your agro and long reach spells mean you can chain pull and keep agro without leaving many camps.  Very nice xp pulling class.  The only alt I'm seriously twinking and will eventually raise up is an SK.  I love the SK class.<br>
<br>
Puller is more of a person skill than a class skill.  Assuming the puller has access to any class, there are times I'd choose SK, times I'd choose monk, times I'd choose any number of classes: war, bard, ranger, druid, enchanter, cleric, paladin, etc. etc..<br>
<br>
The only real advantage the monk class has at pulling is that we have a better chance at surviving some dumb stunt than other classes.  This gives monks more oportunities to learn how to pull than others and provides for safer pulls.  Monk FD is like puller training-wheels. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm43.showMessageRange?topicID=208.topic&start=1&stop=20>1</a> <b>2</b>  </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm43.showPrevMessage?topicID=208.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm43.showNextMessage?topicID=208.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm43.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=208.topic&index=22><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/classic/addReply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"><a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm43.threadControl?topicID=208.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm43.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=208.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/subscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to receive email notification of replies"> Click to receive email notification of replies</a> <br>  <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm43.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=208.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/unsubscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to stop receiving email notification of replies"> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies</a> <br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http